451
00:23:29,180 --> 00:23:30,819
[SPEAKER_02] A to je upravo na onom koraku više,

452
00:23:30,819 --> 00:23:32,160
[SPEAKER_02] a to se može isključivo

453
00:23:32,160 --> 00:23:33,619
