455
00:23:34,799 --> 00:23:36,539
[SPEAKER_02] I na koncu,

456
00:23:36,539 --> 00:23:38,240
[SPEAKER_02] zaključujući nekoliko riječi

457
00:23:38,240 --> 00:23:39,279
[SPEAKER_02] i misli o ovoj knjizi,

458
00:23:39,279 --> 00:23:42,400
[SPEAKER_02] principi o kojima se ne pregovara

459
00:23:42,400 --> 00:23:45,319
[SPEAKER_02] nisu set nekakvih proizvodnjih

460
00:23:45,319 --> 00:23:46,900
[SPEAKER_02] određenih načela

461
00:23:46,900 --> 00:23:49,119
