475
00:24:11,440 --> 00:24:13,400
[SPEAKER_02] oni su naprotivi temelje

476
00:24:13,400 --> 00:24:15,180
[SPEAKER_02] kršćanskog djelovanja,

477
00:24:15,720 --> 00:24:16,980
[SPEAKER_02] koja čovjek nije izmislio,

478
00:24:16,980 --> 00:24:21,180
[SPEAKER_02] nego su ona dio objavljene istine čovjeku.

479
00:24:21,180 --> 00:24:22,960
[SPEAKER_02] Pitanje života,

480
00:24:22,960 --> 00:24:24,839
[SPEAKER_02] pitanje obitelji

481
00:24:24,839 --> 00:24:26,700
[SPEAKER_02] i pitanje odgoja djece

482
00:24:26,700 --> 00:24:29,279
[SPEAKER_02] na koje osobito naglasak stavlja

483
00:24:29,279 --> 00:24:30,519
[SPEAKER_02] autor Možić.

484
00:24:30,519 --> 00:24:33,839
