[SPEAKER_02] i njegova budućnost.

495
00:24:49,559 --> 00:24:51,400
[SPEAKER_02] Okrenimo se oko sebe,

496
00:24:51,400 --> 00:24:52,920
[SPEAKER_02] pogledajmo škole,

497
00:24:52,920 --> 00:24:54,700
