[SPEAKER_02] na koji način se to razvija,

504
00:25:08,460 --> 00:25:12,259
[SPEAKER_02] koje su depresivne faze u životu odraslih,

505
00:25:12,259 --> 00:25:15,380
[SPEAKER_02] srednjovječnih, onih mladih,

506
00:25:15,380 --> 00:25:16,819
[SPEAKER_02] kolika nam je depresija,

507
00:25:16,819 --> 00:25:19,039
[SPEAKER_02] dakle, kod onih u podmakloj dobi,

508
00:25:19,039 --> 00:25:21,460
[SPEAKER_02] na koji način se dogodila ta tranzicija vjere,

509
00:25:21,700 --> 00:25:22,440
[SPEAKER_02] da li se dogodila,

510
00:25:22,440 --> 00:25:24,740
[SPEAKER_02] evo to su sve pitanje o kojima se može raspravljati.

511
00:25:24,740 --> 00:25:26,720
[SPEAKER_02] Dio je to stvarnosti,

512
00:25:26,720 --> 00:25:27,500
