532
00:26:13,880 --> 00:26:15,839
[SPEAKER_02] ako ti nećeš ispovijediti vjeru

533
00:26:15,839 --> 00:26:19,200
[SPEAKER_02] i dati razloge onoga u što ti vjeruješ,

534
00:26:19,200 --> 00:26:20,819
